- Dorajaki.

9
00:04:39,032 --> 00:04:42,092
Prekini da se glupiraš.
- Htela sam da razgovaramo.

10
00:04:42,242 --> 00:04:44,774
Izvini, imam pored sebe bucne drugarice.

11
00:04:44,829 --> 00:04:46,600
Ko je bucan? Ne pricaj bez veze.

12
00:04:46,748 --> 00:04:49,179
Smirite se malo.
- A, što bismo?

13
00:04:49,334 --> 00:04:51,251
Malo tiše, stvarno.

14
00:04:52,045 --> 00:04:52,932
Pokušavam da razgovaram.

15
00:04:53,087 --> 00:04:55,519
Sva je pocrvenela...vrlo je sumnjivo.

16
00:04:55,674 --> 00:04:57,228
Nazvacu te kasnije.

17
00:04:57,384 --> 00:04:59,428
Ma, to je slucajno.
- Jeste.

18
00:04:59,678 --> 00:05:01,070
Izvini, zdravo.

19
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:03,056
Prekinula je.
- Nazvace ponovo.

20
00:05:03,598 --> 00:05:05,265
Nisam prekinula, zato prestanite.

21
00:05:06,643 --> 00:05:08,072
Ponovo ce da zove.

22
00:05:08,227 --> 00:05:11,117
Nemoj da nam se tu skrivaš.
- Sumnjivo.

23
00:05:11,271 --> 00:05:12,673
Jako sumnjivo.

24
00:05:13,273 --> 00:05:15,330
Naša nastavnica?
- A, što, pobogu?

25
00:05:15,485 --> 00:05:17,904
Ja sam samo za Sentara zainterersovana.

26
00:05:18,697 --> 00:05:20,419
Ti si se viðala sa njim?
- Nema šanse.

27
00:05:20,574 --> 00:05:22,158
Onaj stariji decko?

28
00:05:23,283 --> 00:05:26,037
Ma, nisam.
- Samo je Sentaro jedan namcor.

29
00:05:26,621 --> 00:05:29,289
A, danas je predivan dan.
- Sacekaj malo!

30
00:05:30,917 --> 00:05:32,836
Rascvetale su se trešnje.

31
00:05:34,294 --> 00:05:37,298
Ima polena u mom dorajakiju.

32
00:05:37,799 --> 00:05:39,968
Šta si nam to uradio, Sentaro?

33
00:05:40,301 --> 00:05:41,731
Nepoznate supstance.

34
00:05:41,886 --> 00:05:43,972
Zagaðeno je.

35
00:05:46,558 --> 00:05:47,942
Baš je odvratno.

36
00:05:49,102 --> 00:05:51,167
Dacu vam sve ovo, ako odete odavde.

37
00:05:51,312 --> 00:05:53,314
Sjajno!
- Hvala vam!

38
00:05:57,318 --> 00:05:59,028
Hvala.
- U zdravlje!

39
00:05:59,529 --> 00:06:01,698
Vidimo se!
- Cao, cao!

40
00:06:03,241 --> 00:06:05,326
Cao, Sentaro.
- O, Vakana!

41
00:06:09,623 --> 00:06:10,940
Zdravo.

42
00:06:19,633 --> 00:06:21,084
Stiže.

43
00:06:47,744 --> 00:06:49,187
Izvoli...

44
00:07:10,391 --> 00:07:11,692
Ovaj...

45
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:14,921
Dobar dan.

46
00:07:15,730 --> 00:07:19,250
Videla sam vašu poruku,
za pomocnika...

47
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,403
Stvarno nema ogranicenja
u vezi godina?

48
00:07:21,611 --> 00:07:22,987
Da.

49
00:07:23,404 --> 00:07:24,864
Ja, ovaj...

50
00:07:25,365 --> 00:07:27,576
Da li mislite, da bih ja mogla?

51
00:07:30,244 --> 00:07:34,248
Oduvek sam htela da radim
baš ovakav posao.

52
00:07:37,336 --> 00:07:40,737
Koliko imate godina?
- Napunicu 76 ove godine.

53
00:07:44,384 --> 00:07:45,885
Samo, mi ne placamo mnogo.

54
00:07:46,303 --> 00:07:49,013
Samo 600 jena.

55
00:07:52,016 --> 00:07:55,479
Oh...300 jena na sat
je sasvim dovoljno.

56
00:07:55,770 --> 00:07:58,540
300 jena je u redu.
- 300 jena?

57
00:07:58,690 --> 00:07:59,991
Da!

58
00:08:00,441 --> 00:08:01,842
Pa...

59
00:08:02,443 --> 00:08:04,445
Ne mislim da ce biti moguce.

60
00:08:14,623 --> 00:08:17,626
Ja se zovem Tokue Joši.

61
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,922
Bolece vas jako leða.

62
00:08:27,302 --> 00:08:28,703
Ovo je teško...

63
00:08:29,429 --> 00:08:32,724
Ovo je teže, nego što izgleda.

64
00:08:34,475 --> 00:08:35,876
Uzmite.

65
00:08:44,235 --> 00:08:45,686
Aha...

66
00:08:47,488 --> 00:08:48,990
Ja castim.

67
00:08:50,492 --> 00:08:51,893
Molim vas.

68
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:00,969
Da li vi znate...

69
00:09:01,586 --> 00:09:03,338
ovo trešnjino drvo...

70
00:09:04,589 --> 00:09:06,466
ko ga je posadio?

71
00:09:12,347 --> 00:09:14,223
Ja baš nisam iz ovog kraja...

72
00:09:20,063 --> 00:09:21,522
Hvala, navraticu ja opet.

73
00:09:32,033 --> 00:09:33,442
Sinko...

74
00:09:48,342 --> 00:09:50,551
Ostaci.
- Hvala vam.

75
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:11,448
Taj...posao pomocnika...

76
00:10:11,823 --> 00:10:13,533
mogu li ja to da radim?

77
00:10:14,326 --> 00:10:17,578
Pa...kada budeš krenula
u srednju školu.

78
00:10:18,788 --> 00:10:21,333
Ja možda i necu da idem
u srednju školu.

79
00:10:26,421 --> 00:10:28,006
Molim vas, racunajte na mene.

80
00:10:32,593 --> 00:10:33,894
Hvala ti.

81
00:11:48,294 --> 00:11:49,879
Ne, Marvi.

82
00:11:52,006 --> 00:11:53,674
Moraš da budeš tih.

83
00:12:23,997 --> 00:12:25,406
Dobar dan...

84
00:12:27,083 --> 00:12:28,492
Šta je to?

85
00:12:28,709 --> 00:12:30,110
Zdravo!

86
00:12:34,715 --> 00:12:37,677
Ovo je, kako ja pišem svoje ime.

87
00:12:42,723 --> 00:12:45,310
Samo, ja ne mogu da vas primim.
Žao mi je.

88
00:12:47,771 --> 00:12:52,733
Kao što možete da vidite,
ruke su mi malo obogaljene.

89
00:12:53,443 --> 00:12:59,433
Tako da...moglo bi da bude i manje,
200 je sasvim dovoljno.

90
00:13:01,993 --> 00:13:04,287
Za šta?
- Za sat rada.

91
00:13:05,163 --> 00:13:06,390
Nije u tome problem.

92
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:11,044
Da li vi sami pravite taj fil
od pasulja, sinko?

93
00:13:12,753 --> 00:13:14,172
Pa, to je...

94
00:13:14,839 --> 00:13:16,150
proizvodna tajna.

95
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:18,759
Kako to mislite "proizvodna"?

96
00:13:19,344 --> 00:13:21,346
U ovom malom lokalu?

97
00:13:27,686 --> 00:13:29,354
Dakle, ja...

98
00:13:30,730 --> 00:13:33,232
ja sam probala vaš dorajaki.

99
00:13:34,693 --> 00:13:38,779
Mišljenja sam da vaše palacinke
nisu loše.

100
00:13:39,323 --> 00:13:40,749
Ali...

101
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:44,077
fil od pasulja nije...nije baš dobar.

102
00:13:44,619 --> 00:13:46,787
Nije to lako napraviti.

103
00:13:47,581 --> 00:13:48,802
Da li ste to ikada praviti?

104
00:13:48,957 --> 00:13:52,419
Ja to oduvek pravim.
Celih 50 godina.

105
00:13:52,793 --> 00:13:54,145
50 godina?

106
00:13:54,295 --> 00:13:56,797
Jeste...pola veka.

107
00:13:57,757 --> 00:14:01,553
Za fil od pasulja treba
osecaj, sinko.

108
00:14:03,096 --> 00:14:05,806
Ja ne mogu da vas zaposlim,
žao mi je.

109
00:14:12,689 --> 00:14:15,191
Evo, probajte malo ovoga.

110
00:14:16,025 --> 00:14:17,426
Šta je to?

111
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:21,448
Šta je ovo?

112
00:14:44,346 --> 00:14:45,846
Gusti fil od pasulja.

113
00:16:06,886 --> 00:16:08,287
Ja se izvinjavam.

114
00:16:11,516 --> 00:16:13,267
Ulaziš unutra?

115
00:16:14,935 --> 00:16:16,279
Zdravo!

116
00:16:24,571 --> 00:16:25,980
Dobro vece.

117
00:16:26,114 --> 00:16:27,415
Šta?

118
00:16:30,494 --> 00:16:31,803
Izvinjavam se.

119
00:16:33,413 --> 00:16:36,023
Došla si da nešto jedeš?
- Jesam.

120
00:16:38,877 --> 00:16:41,254
Jednu flašu piva, i...

121
00:16:43,131 --> 00:16:44,591
jedan tempura obrok.

122
00:16:47,927 --> 00:16:50,013
I ja cu da uzmem tempuru.

123
00:16:50,555 --> 00:16:51,898
Tempura.

124
00:16:52,891 --> 00:16:54,358
I, pepeljaru, molim.

125
00:16:59,314 --> 00:17:00,757
Evo, izvolite.

126
00:17:04,653 --> 00:17:06,162
On ti je prijatelj?

127
00:17:06,613 --> 00:17:10,450
Da...bio je u mom klubu u školi.

128
00:17:11,992 --> 00:17:13,453
Sada je u srednjoj školi.

129
00:17:15,246 --> 00:17:17,998
Evo ga vaše pivo, za pocetak.

130
00:17:45,652 --> 00:17:47,446
Ta žena, koja je svracala...

131
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:51,431
tražeci posao...

132
00:17:57,914 --> 00:17:59,499
dolazila je kasnije ponovo.

133
00:18:02,043 --> 00:18:06,598
Donela je malo gustog fila od pasulja,
koji je sama napravila.

134
00:18:07,841 --> 00:18:09,092
Bio je neverovatan.

135
00:18:12,052 --> 00:18:13,347
Prosto sam zatecen.

136
00:18:14,598 --> 00:18:15,990
Kako to?

137
00:18:18,810 --> 00:18:20,562
Taj ukus, miris...

138
00:18:22,814 --> 00:18:25,734
Potpuno drugaciji, od onog,
koji ja koristim.

139
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:36,076
Trebalo bi da je pustite da pokuša.

140
00:18:38,705 --> 00:18:40,832
Ona je htela da radi.

141
00:20:14,426 --> 00:20:15,819
O, dobar dan.

142
00:20:16,303 --> 00:20:17,754
Drago mi je što vas vidim.

143
00:20:20,181 --> 00:20:22,559
Ovi cvetovi su svi opali.

144
00:20:23,101 --> 00:20:25,061
Da, jesu.

145
00:20:26,896 --> 00:20:29,983
Evo, mašu nam svojim rukama.

146
00:20:30,274 --> 00:20:31,901
Zdravo, zdravo, zdravo!

147
00:20:32,527 --> 00:20:34,112
Zdravo, zdravo, zdravo!

148
00:20:48,042 --> 00:20:50,557
Vaš gusti fil od pasulja
je bio izvrstan.

149
00:20:50,712 --> 00:20:52,839
A, probali ste ga?

150
00:20:56,259 --> 00:20:57,660
Tako da...

151
00:20:58,136 --> 00:21:01,806
ako vam ne smeta, da li biste
hteli da mi pomažete?

152
00:21:02,557 --> 00:21:03,967
Doðite da sednete.

153
00:21:06,311 --> 00:21:08,563
Dakle, au...

154
00:21:09,063 --> 00:21:10,448
Šefe...

155
00:21:12,651 --> 00:21:14,193
Au, šefe.

156
00:21:15,235 --> 00:21:17,237
Hvala vam.
- Nema na cemu.

157
00:21:17,989 --> 00:21:19,390
Molim vas...

158
00:21:24,244 --> 00:21:28,350
Možete li vi da podižete šerpe? Potrebna
je snaga, da bi se napravio taj fil.

159
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:32,252
Pusticu vas, da podižete šerpe.

160
00:21:33,253 --> 00:21:34,655
To je u redu.

161
00:21:35,131 --> 00:21:37,687
Izvinjavam se što pitam,
da li možete da rukujete kašikom?

162
00:21:37,842 --> 00:21:39,260
Da, naravno.

163
00:21:39,928 --> 00:21:43,723
Vi ste rekli pre neki dan,
da su vam ruke malo...

164
00:21:44,264 --> 00:21:48,520
One, ustvari, nisu zaista problem,
sem to kako izgledaju.

165
00:21:50,564 --> 00:21:53,953
Sve vas to pitam, jer cete vi
da pravite taj fil od pasulja.

166
00:21:54,108 --> 00:21:57,277
Au, stvarno...

167
00:21:57,571 --> 00:22:01,908
Ja cu da budem sposobna,
da ovde radim!

168
00:22:10,041 --> 00:22:11,491
Hvala vam.

169
00:22:18,383 --> 00:22:21,147
Napišite broj svog telefona,
ili boj svog mobilnog.

170
00:22:21,302 --> 00:22:23,137
Moj telefon...

171
00:22:23,262 --> 00:22:27,559
Ja nemam telefon...
ja komuniciram pismima.

172
00:22:28,309 --> 00:22:32,356
Necu ja da kasnim na posao.
Ja ujutru ustajem pre ptica.

173
00:22:32,606 --> 00:22:34,023
Ne radi se o tome...

174
00:22:35,609 --> 00:22:37,819
Pa, onda...

175
00:22:38,319 --> 00:22:39,729
Hvala vam.

176
00:22:41,322 --> 00:22:43,214
Pitala sam se...

177
00:22:43,367 --> 00:22:47,537
Da li vi sami pravite vaš
fil od pasulja?

178
00:22:48,329 --> 00:22:49,730
Dakle, ovaj...

179
00:22:52,333 --> 00:22:55,294
Mnogo puta sam pokušao.

180
00:22:55,587 --> 00:22:57,559
Ali je to stvarno jako teško.

181
00:22:57,714 --> 00:23:02,051
Ili ima ukus nagorelog,
ili se nekako zgrudva.

182
00:23:02,636 --> 00:23:04,220
Meni je to baš teško...

183
00:23:06,180 --> 00:23:07,548
Za mene...

184
00:23:08,350 --> 00:23:09,976
Fil od pasulja...

185
00:23:12,353 --> 00:23:15,940
Radnja se otvara u 11.
Ja pocinjem pripreme u 9.

186
00:23:16,190 --> 00:23:17,558
A, fil od pasulja...

187
00:23:18,192 --> 00:23:19,503
Šta je ovo?

188
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,947
Fil od pasulja?
- Jeste.

189
00:23:24,365 --> 00:23:25,766
To je to.

190
00:23:26,701 --> 00:23:28,186
Fil od pasulja.

191
00:23:28,369 --> 00:23:29,770
Šta?

192
00:23:30,914 --> 00:23:32,677
Porucena masa.
- Porucena masa?

193
00:23:32,832 --> 00:23:35,544
Zašto? Kako ste samo mogli?

194
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:38,380
Mi to oduvek ovako nabavljamo.

195
00:23:38,672 --> 00:23:40,081
Oduvek?

196
00:23:43,259 --> 00:23:47,556
Fil od pasulja je duša dorajakija.

197
00:23:48,807 --> 00:23:51,393
Kako samo možete da to tako
olako prihvatate?

198
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:54,563
Oni to donose, cim mi porucimo.

199
00:23:56,565 --> 00:23:59,818
Vi treba da pravite svoj
sopstveni fil od pasulja.

200
00:24:02,236 --> 00:24:07,003
Ako se radnja otvara u 11,
sutra ujutru,

201
00:24:07,158 --> 00:24:11,746
mi cemo poceti sa pripremama, pre nego
što gospodin Sunce promoli svoje lice.

202
00:24:12,497 --> 00:24:13,865
Gospodin Sunce?

203
00:24:14,791 --> 00:24:17,418
Jeste, gospodin Sunce.

204
00:24:55,957 --> 00:24:57,325
Dobro jutro.

205
00:25:00,629 --> 00:25:03,464
Tu je bilo drvo sa malim trešnjama.

206
00:25:04,549 --> 00:25:05,917
Zar je bilo?

207
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,359
Voze li autobusi ovako rano?

208
00:25:08,512 --> 00:25:11,431
U redu je, ne brinite se za to.

209
00:25:11,598 --> 00:25:12,966
Onda, dobro.

210
00:25:20,481 --> 00:25:23,041
Izvolite.
- Hvala.

211
00:25:26,446 --> 00:25:27,847
Ovde je.

212
00:25:43,129 --> 00:25:44,673
A...dobro je.

213
00:25:49,844 --> 00:25:53,557
Šefe, da li ste ih pregledali,
pre nego što ste ih potopili?

214
00:25:54,223 --> 00:25:55,266
Šta to?

215
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:57,518
Azuki pasulj.

216
00:26:04,359 --> 00:26:05,819
Evo, pogledajte.

217
00:26:05,944 --> 00:26:08,279
Neki od njih nisu dobri.

218
00:26:09,614 --> 00:26:11,783
Evo, kao ovaj...vidite?

219
00:26:12,533 --> 00:26:13,902
Izvinjavam se.

220
00:26:14,035 --> 00:26:15,536
Zašto se izvinjavate?

221
00:26:15,704 --> 00:26:17,180
Ne znam...

222
00:26:19,583 --> 00:26:20,950
Dobro, dobro.

223
00:26:21,543 --> 00:26:24,087
Sipajte ih u bakarni lonac.

224
00:26:27,716 --> 00:26:29,604
Pogledajte samo boju vode.

225
00:26:29,759 --> 00:26:32,429
Stvarno...dosta toga se ocedilo.

226
00:26:37,601 --> 00:26:39,531
U redu, dobro je, dobro.

227
00:26:39,686 --> 00:26:43,357
Prespite ih u cediljku.

228
00:26:49,363 --> 00:26:50,939
Pravo unutra?
- Da, da...pažljivo.

229
00:26:54,326 --> 00:26:55,552
Da, ovde.

230
00:26:55,702 --> 00:26:57,329
Vrelo je, zar ne?

231
00:26:57,912 --> 00:27:00,581
Isperite ovo.
Neka se properu.

232
00:27:03,710 --> 00:27:05,111
Dobro?

233
00:27:07,588 --> 00:27:11,589
Držite ovo...neka se isperu,
evo ovako.

234
00:27:12,093 --> 00:27:16,597
Morate da ih potpuno isperete,
inace ce pasulj biti gorak.

235
00:27:17,598 --> 00:27:18,758
Dobro je.

236
00:27:18,908 --> 00:27:21,436
Vratite ih nazad u bakarni lonac.

237
00:27:23,647 --> 00:27:26,547
A, sada, voda...cista voda.

238
00:27:26,691 --> 00:27:28,059
Izvinite.

239
00:27:29,152 --> 00:27:30,520
Dobro je tako.

240
00:27:31,571 --> 00:27:33,463
Da sipam unutra?
- Da, sipajte to unutra.

241
00:27:33,614 --> 00:27:35,586
Polako, nežno.

