285
00:31:41,154 --> 00:31:42,863
A, pa, oko 2 sata.

286
00:31:43,323 --> 00:31:44,724
Dva sata!

287
00:31:47,577 --> 00:31:49,162
Dva sata...

288
00:32:25,490 --> 00:32:27,758
Evo, sada je kriticni momenat.

289
00:32:27,908 --> 00:32:29,756
