297
00:32:51,933 --> 00:32:54,478
Pomerajte kašiku pažljivo.

298
00:32:54,935 --> 00:32:57,000
To je to, nemojte da ih zdrobite.

299
00:32:57,146 --> 00:32:59,899
Malo, po malo...

300
00:32:59,940 --> 00:33:02,944
Malo, po malo, koliko je to?

301
00:33:03,069 --> 00:33:06,365
Malo...je malo.

302
