Evo ga.

311
00:33:35,519 --> 00:33:36,770
A, ovo dobro izgleda.

312
00:33:40,981 --> 00:33:43,079
A, sada, za sledece...

313
00:33:43,234 --> 00:33:44,205
Mogu li da operem ruke?

314
00:33:44,361 --> 00:33:47,000
Pa, naravno, šta cekate uopšte?

315
00:33:47,155 --> 00:33:49,073
Pa, ovaj...

316
00:33:49,990 --> 00:33:51,451
Aha, slavina? Dobro.

317
00:33:52,494 --> 00:33:54,663
Evo ga.
- Pažljivo.

318
00:33:56,289 --> 00:33:57,624
Dobro, dobro...

319
00:33:57,998 --> 00:33:59,292
Sjajno izgleda.

320
00:34:42,752 --> 00:34:44,338
Još uvek je pomalo vruce.

321
00:34:48,967 --> 00:34:50,368
Da li je dobro?

322
00:34:50,552 --> 00:34:52,011
Još uvek je vruce.

323
00:35:19,581 --> 00:35:21,583
Pa, šta mislite, šefe?

324
00:35:23,502 --> 00:35:25,211
Nikad nisam jeo ovako nešto.

325
00:35:34,262 --> 00:35:36,222
O, što je ukusno...

326
00:35:36,681 --> 00:35:38,082
Da, jeste.

327
00:35:38,933 --> 00:35:42,396
Konacno sam našao dorajaki,
koji ja mogu da pojedem.

328
00:35:43,772 --> 00:35:45,173
Ha?

329
