362
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,830
Ovaj fil od pasulja je izvanredan.

363
00:37:53,985 --> 00:37:55,790
Zar jeste?
- Svi to kažu.

364
00:37:55,945 --> 00:37:57,087
Hvala vam.

365
00:37:57,237 --> 00:37:59,658
Baš je ukusan, zar ne?

366
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:01,651
Imate li još jedan?

367
00:38:01,910 --> 00:38:03,077
Hvala vam.

368
