441
00:44:04,605 --> 00:44:06,032
Evo, izvolite.

442
00:44:06,190 --> 00:44:08,151
Hvala vam.
- Hvala vama.

443
00:44:08,985 --> 00:44:10,779
Ovo je sjajno!

444
00:44:40,850 --> 00:44:42,113
Imaš li minut?

445
00:44:42,268 --> 00:44:44,103
Šta, proveravate svoju radnju?

446
00:44:47,482 --> 00:44:49,539
Ljudi pricaju ovde o necemu.

447
00:44:49,693 --> 00:44:52,111
U vezi tvoje pomocnice...

448
00:44:52,653 --> 00:44:54,113
A, Tokue.

449
00:44:55,407 --> 00:44:56,825
