456
00:45:19,473 --> 00:45:21,891
Sada, kada ste spomenuli, jesu malo...

457
00:45:22,517 --> 00:45:26,020
Moja prijateljica kaže,
da to mora da je lepra.

458
00:45:29,148 --> 00:45:31,860
