dezinfikovala.

485
00:47:27,808 --> 00:47:29,018
Ali, gospoðo...

486
00:47:30,937 --> 00:47:32,772
ova prodavnica je prosto
eksplodirala...

487
00:47:33,773 --> 00:47:39,070
i to sve zahvaljujuci Tokue
i njenom filu od pasulja.

488
00:47:39,237 --> 00:47:41,656
Znam ja to.

