737
01:15:26,988 --> 01:15:29,672
Dala je otkaz.
- Zaista?

738
01:15:43,838 --> 01:15:45,223
Šta je to?

739
01:15:46,174 --> 01:15:48,509
Ja, ovaj...

740
01:15:49,510 --> 01:15:51,512
