741
01:15:51,888 --> 01:15:53,289
Pobegla?

742
01:15:54,933 --> 01:15:56,334
Kada to?

743
01:15:57,352 --> 01:15:58,819
Jutros.

744
01:15:59,979 --> 01:16:01,522
Baš ovog jutra...

745
01:16:09,739 --> 01:16:11,532
On se zove Marvi.

746
01:16:13,993 --> 01:16:18,498
Mi živimo u stanu, 
a kucni ljubimci su zabranjeni.

747
