790
01:22:20,944 --> 01:22:22,487
Došli ste oboje.

791
01:22:26,325 --> 01:22:28,909
Ovo je Marvi.

792
01:22:30,911 --> 01:22:33,039
Ti si predivno žut, Marvi.

793
01:22:35,916 --> 01:22:37,251
Marvi...

794
